co.cask.coopr.store.provisioner

Class LocalFilePluginStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.coopr.store.provisioner.LocalFilePluginStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PluginStore

    public class LocalFilePluginStore
extends Object
implements PluginStore
    Plugin store that writes resources to the local file system. Modules are namespaced by the data directory given in the configuration, plugin type, plugin type id, resource type, name, and version.

      • getResourceOutputStream

        public OutputStream getResourceOutputStream(Account account,
                                   ResourceType type,
                                   String name,
                                   int version)
                                     throws IOException
        Get an output stream for the given resource. Files are namespaced by base data directory, plugin type, plugin name, resource type, resource name, and resource version. For example, version 2 of resource 'hadoop' of type 'cookbook'' for automator type 'chef-solo' with data directory '/var/coopr/data/plugins' will be written to '/var/coopr/data/plugins/automatortypes/chef-solo/cookbook/hadoop/2'.
        Specified by:
        getResourceOutputStream in interface PluginStore
        Parameters:
        account - Account that owns the plugin resource
        type - Type of resource
        name - Name of the resource being written
        version - Version of the resource being written
        Returns:
        Output stream for the file
        Throws:
        IOException - if there was an error creating the file
